overview: The Ultimate Crest Batangueño Productions present to you, “DIMALUPIG”, an inspiring career advocacy film about the heart and soul of the Filipino seafarer. We have a lot to learn about who puts the food on our tables, who runs most of the world economy. And this film, first of its kind, first in history, teaches us, introduces the hidden industry of seafaring to the Filipino youth, through an educational and inspirational docu-fictional drama.
title: Dimalupig
